lines: bde chen ye shes me lce yis
sgrib gnyis bud shing kun sreg pa
bla ma 'khor lo sdom pa yi
zhabs kyi padmor phyag 'tshal lo
oM AH swA hAs yaM shing dang
oM shrI swA hAs bzhun mar dang
oM dzriM swA hAs 'bru dang
oM ku ru ku ru swA hA
tshangs pa lha rnams dag byed yin
dkon cog gsum po mnyes byed pa
sa las skyes pa'i 'dab ma'i snying
bdag gi bgegs rnams thams cad ni
zhi dang bkra shis mdzad du gsol
'jig rten dbang phyug tshangs dbang mgon gyi sras
me lha'i rgyal po Tak+kis dbang bskur ba
shes rab mchog gis nyon mongs thams cad sreg
'dzin byed me lha nyid la rnam par 'dud
tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras
me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog
'byung po yongs su bskyang ba'i phyir
thugs rje'i dbang gis sku sprul pa
rig sngags grub pa'i drang srong tshul
nyon mongs sreg pa'i shes rab 'od
bskal pa'i me bzhin gzi brjid 'bar
mngon shes rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan
thabs kyis sprul pa'i theg pa bcibs
rig sngags gsung zhing bgrang 'phreng 'dzin
bdud rtsi'i bcud ldan guN+De bsnams
chos kyi bdud rtsi yongs la bsil
nyes pa'i skyon bral tshangs par spyod
'jig rten gnas kyang mya ngan 'das
zhi ba brnyes kyang thugs rje che
de bas bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal
gang yang bdag blo rmongs pa yis
zhes sogs kyis nongs pa bzod par gsol
he ru ka'i yig brgya brjod la
bdag la dngos grub mchog stsol la
mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di snoms la
zhes sogs kyis 'phrin las bcol
mchod yon phul te bzod par gsol
'dod don la 'phrin las bcol
rang gi don dang gzhan gyi don
sgrub byed bsreg bya za ba gshegs
ji bzhin dus su tshur byon zhing
bdag gi dngos grub thams cad bsgrubs
dpal ldan 'khor lo sdom pa'i sbyin sreg gi
phyag len dri med cung zad 'dir bkod pas
sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i thab tu tsaN+Da li
haM yig mar gyi thigs pas legs bran pas
bde stong lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes med
gnyis snang 'khrul pa'i bud shing kun bsregs nas
sku gsum rin cen gzhal med nyams dga' bar
'gro kun bla med bde la spyod gyur cig
bstan pa'i sbyin bdag chen po 'khor bcas kyang
sku tshe ring zhing chab srid rgyas pa dang
zab lam rdo rje theg pa'i dga' ston gyis
chos rgyal rigs ldan rnams dang mtshungs par shog
